    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience with every component functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a collector or anyone seeking a vehicle in showroom-quality condition.",
